==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Laze
<hw>Laze</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To waste in sloth; to spend, as
time, in idleness; <as>as, to <ex>laze</ex> away whole days</as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lazily</ent>⟦br⟧
